stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_decode: decode opcode 0x1e (CLZ)
    q_decode --> q_check_gas: check gas remaining
    q_check_gas --> q_oog: gas < 5
    q_oog --> [*]: revert out-of-gas
    q_check_gas --> q_deduct: gas >= 5
    q_deduct --> q_check_stack: deduct 5 gas
    q_check_stack --> q_underflow: stack depth < 1
    q_underflow --> [*]: revert stack underflow
    q_check_stack --> q_execute: stack depth >= 1
    q_execute --> q_pop: pop x
    q_pop --> q_compute: compute clz(x)
    q_compute --> q_push: push result
    q_push --> [*]: advance program counter
